Hello this is written using vim 
vim is application to create and edit files in linux !
1. sudo apt install vim
2. in terminal type vim filename
3. enter i to insert data
4. press esc to escape  
5. enter :w to execute
6. hit enter to save file
7. for exit -------------- after saving -------------------
8. hit escape 
9.press :q to quit

10. if there is no need to save data after updating or other scenario 
	press escape
	enter :q!
    not save updated values  

